main event: A document from Project Blue Book in 1965 contains various images of unidentified flying objects (UFOs) and related material.
interesting points: The report includes a black and white photograph of a metallic or reflective spherical object that appears suspended in the air., One image shows a dark, starry sky with faint bright spots., There is an image depicting a blurry, dark object against a dark background., Several pages contain unidentifiable dark images believed to represent UFOs., The images are labeled as 'UNCLASSIFIED' by the FOREIGN TECHNOLOGY DIVISION, AFSC.
witness description: The report contains scans and images rather than eyewitness descriptions.
